## 3. Avatar

Sirkulær bilde- eller initial-visning.

**Props:** `src?`, `alt?`, `name?` (for initialer-fallback), `size` (`xs` | `sm` | `md` | `lg` | `xl`).

**CSS:**
```css
@utility avatar {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
